Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.49,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那些羨煞旁人的事 對我們來說是重要的交流方式
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我才不管這些常識
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.21,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你們倒是讓我也看看那些羨煞旁人的事啊
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看你個鬼啊
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老公
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那個…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.81,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯…早安
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}昨…昨晚真是火熱呢
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是 並沒有到那種地步
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.99,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的 真的啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小司你和她說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早安 千歲
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太陽曬屁股了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:35.21,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哎呀哎呀 今天的睡姿也是如此性感呢
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}千歲 早上啦
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以說你為什麼要把臉貼這麼近啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:49.94,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因為你完全不起床啊
Dialogue: 3,0:18:53.02,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然後…
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我會起床的 離我遠點
Dialogue: 3,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我來幫你換衣服吧
Dialogue: 3,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}笨蛋笨蛋 你把手往哪伸啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我幫你脫衣服哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}誰要你幫啊
Dialogue: 3,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}別害羞嘛
Dialogue: 3,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這並非性騷擾
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這女僕 只是個天然色
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}話說剛才我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.26,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}星空和小司昨晚好像非常火熱哦
Dialogue: 3,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什麼意思
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不 剛才…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:35.82,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我去澡堂洗澡的時候
Dialogue: 3,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}碰巧聽到他們在說這些
Dialogue: 3,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你早上還去那裡洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不…不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}反…反正他們是夫妻 做這些不是很正常嗎…
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}這些指的是什麼事？
Dialogue: 3,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}請告訴我他們做了哪些火熱的事
Dialogue: 3,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不不 又太近了
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是在床上牽手擁抱那檔子事啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是我平時對千歲做的那些事嗎
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能不能說人話
Dialogue: 3,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}比起那些
Dialogue: 3,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更加激烈
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}激烈…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}簡單來說
Dialogue: 3,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是夫妻關係和睦吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是啊
Dialogue: 3,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯嗯 關係和睦是好事
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我和歐羅拉也是關係和睦的好朋友？
Dialogue: 3,0:20:35.79,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}算…算是吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼
Dialogue: 3,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今晚就牽著手一起睡吧
Dialogue: 3,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也行…
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}開玩笑的 玩笑玩笑
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那麼 晚安啦
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}魔性的女人
Dialogue: 3,0:21:08.83,0:21:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明…明天也要早起 差不多該睡了呢
Dialogue: 3,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是…是啊
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回頭讓小要看到我們沒睡好
Dialogue: 3,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不知道她又會說什麼
Dialogue: 3,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是啊
